item.title: Adding a custom
item.dc:creator: @WestSideMass WestSideMass
item.description:
@WestSideMass wrote:

Add the Drop and the Inventory model into your model folder (client sided).
Compile + Login to your server. Type “Add Model #” and “Add Model #”.
Add the integers into Class8.Java, and Compile.
Login to your server and use the ::pickup command to get your cape.
To make it equip in the cape spot, add it in Item.java, or Item4.java on your server side. Add it under public static int capes.

Read full topic
